# --- data files ---
# The data/ folder currently contains BOTH mock and real data:
#   - mock_cases_67.csv, mock_cases_157.csv     (synthetic, safe)
#   - main_cases_67.csv, other_cases_157.csv    (real, cleared for publication)
# These four files are intentionally tracked. The patterns below are
# safeguards against accidentally committing NEW confidential files
# under conventional names — review any new CSV before adding it.
data/real_*.csv
data/*_confidential*.csv
data/*_raw*.csv
data/*_pii*.csv
